<plot>The sun doesn't shine on this Atlantic City. It exists in dive bars and strip joints. In the shadow of the Casinos, is a world of backroom deals that can end a life over less money than the price of a bus ticket home. Nobody chooses to come here, this where they end up. Atlantic City Serenade is about the Price we pay for the choices we make in the quest for power over our own inner demons. It is told through the eyes of the members of several dysfunctional "families", desperate associations of lost souls bound by loyalty, fear or both.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?050091</url></doc>
